snippet.title: Predator for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Predator is a rather unique clone of Joust.

Instead of attacking from above, you instead shoot (in this case) birds. You can also collect eggs and leaves for points.
